{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CYndGNuuCHDbcwipcJZBaG","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# AGENTS.md - AI Coding Agent Reference\n     2→\n     3→This file provides essential information for AI coding agents working on this project. It contains project-specific details, conventions, and guidelines that complement the README.\n     4→\n     5→---\n     6→\n     7→## Project Overview\n     8→\n     9→**Next.js Admin Dashboard Starter** is a production-ready admin dashboard template built with:\n    10→\n    11→- **Framework**: Next.js 16 (App Router)\n    12→- **Language**: TypeScript 5.7\n    13→- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4\n    14→- **UI Components**: shadcn/ui (New York style)\n    15→- **Authentication**: Clerk (with Organizations/Billing support)\n    16→- **Error Tracking**: Sentry\n    17→- **Charts**: Recharts\n    18→- **Containerization**: Docker (Node.js & Bun Dockerfiles)\n    19→- **Package Manager**: Bun (preferred) or npm\n    20→\n    21→The project follows a feature-based folder structure designed for scalability in SaaS applications, internal tools, and admin panels.\n    22→\n    23→---\n    24→\n    25→## Technology Stack Details\n    26→\n    27→### Core Framework & Runtime\n    28→\n    29→- Next.js 16.0.10 with App Router\n    30→- React 19.2.0\n    31→- TypeScript 5.7.2 with strict mode enabled\n    32→\n    33→### Styling & UI\n    34→\n    35→- Tailwind CSS v4 (using `@import 'tailwindcss'` syntax)\n    36→- PostCSS with `@tailwindcss/postcss` plugin\n    37→- shadcn/ui component library (Radix UI primitives)\n    38→- CSS custom properties for theming (OKLCH color format)\n    39→\n    40→### State Management\n    41→\n    42→- Zustand 5.x for local UI state (chat, kanban, notifications)\n    43→- Nuqs for URL search params state management\n    44→- TanStack Form + Zod for form handling (via `useAppForm` hook)\n    45→\n    46→### Data Fetching & Caching\n    47→\n    48→- TanStack React Query for data fetching, caching, and mutations\n    49→- Server-side prefetching with `HydrationBoundary` + `dehydrate`\n    50→- Client-side `useQuery` + nuqs `shallow: true` for tables (no RSC round-trips on pagination/filter)\n    51→- `useMutation` + `invalidateQueries` for form submissions\n    52→- Query client singleton in `src/lib/query-client.ts`\n    53→\n    54→### Authentication & Authorization\n    55→\n    56→- Clerk for authentication and user management\n    57→- Clerk Organizations for multi-tenant workspaces\n    58→- Clerk Billing for subscription management (B2B)\n    59→- Client-side RBAC for navigation visibility\n    60→\n    61→### Data & APIs\n    62→\n    63→- TanStack Table for data tables\n    64→- TanStack React Query for data fetching and mutations\n    65→- Recharts for analytics/charts\n    66→- Service layer per feature (`api/types.ts` → `api/service.ts` → `api/queries.ts`)\n    67→- Route handlers at `src/app/api/` (for Route Handler or BFF patterns)\n    68→- Mock data in `src/constants/mock-api*.ts` (default, swap via service layer)\n    69→- API client utility in `src/lib/api-client.ts` (for fetch-based patterns)\n    70→\n    71→### Development Tools\n    72→\n    73→- ESLint 8.x with Next.js core-web-vitals config\n    74→- Prettier 3.x with prettier-plugin-tailwindcss\n    75→- Husky for git hooks\n    76→- lint-staged for pre-commit formatting\n    77→\n    78→---\n    79→\n    80→## Project Structure\n    81→\n    82→```\n    83→/src\n    84→├── app/                    # Next.js App Router\n    85→│   ├── auth/              # Authentication routes (sign-in, sign-up)\n    86→│   ├── dashboard/         # Dashboard routes\n    87→│   │   ├── overview/      # Parallel routes (@area_stats, @bar_stats, etc.)\n    88→│   │   ├── product/       # Product management pages\n    89→│   │   ├── kanban/        # Kanban board page\n    90→│   │   ├── chat/          # Messaging page\n    91→│   │   ├── notifications/ # Notifications page\n    92→│   │   ├── workspaces/    # Organization management\n    93→│   │   ├── billing/       # Subscription billing\n    94→│   │   ├── exclusive/     # Pro plan feature example\n    95→│   │   └── profile/       # User profile\n    96→│   ├── api/               # API routes (if any)\n    97→│   ├── layout.tsx         # Root layout with providers\n    98→│   ├── page.tsx           # Landing page\n    99→│   ├── global-error.tsx   # Sentry-integrated error boundary\n   100→│   └── not-found.tsx      # 404 page"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_0133G6eTKKyED961Dh5CjooQ","session_id":"b1ad336c-66a2-4f3f-98dd-2e5d8c4f5736","uuid":"76797a35-2f1a-4434-8776-6ed656692842"}
