{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Stjba2vKnJso5XNcmGzJD3","type":"tool_result","content":"# Better Auth UI - Documentation Links & Setup Information\n\n## Key Documentation Links\n\n- **Main Site**: https://better-auth-ui.com\n- **Installation Guide**: /getting-started/installation\n- **Requirements**: /getting-started/requirements\n- **Demo**: https://newtech.dev/auth/sign-in\n- **Roadmap**: https://betterauthui.featurebase.app/roadmap\n\n## Setup Overview\n\nBetter Auth UI provides \"ready-to-use shadcn/ui styled components for rapidly implementing authentication features in your Next.js and React applications.\"\n\n### Key Features\nThe library emphasizes three main benefits:\n1. **Easy** – Plug and play authentication components\n2. **Customizable** – Fully styled with TailwindCSS and shadcn/ui\n3. **Robust** – Built with modern best practices for React projects\n\n### Before Installation\n\nThe documentation recommends reviewing the **Requirements** page before starting installation to ensure seamless integration of the `@daveyplate/better-auth-ui` library.\n\n### Available Integration Paths\n\nThe documentation covers setup for:\n- Next.js\n- TanStack Start\n- React\n\n## Additional Resources\n\n- **LLMs.txt file**: https://better-auth-ui.com/llms.txt (helps AI understand the auth UI)\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/daveyplate/better-auth-ui\n- **Creator**: @daveycodez"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b1ad336c-66a2-4f3f-98dd-2e5d8c4f5736","uuid":"6b4e01b4-31a6-4e40-b556-0d3094b6bbb3","tool_use_result":{"bytes":134836,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Better Auth UI - Documentation Links & Setup Information\n\n## Key Documentation Links\n\n- **Main Site**: https://better-auth-ui.com\n- **Installation Guide**: /getting-started/installation\n- **Requirements**: /getting-started/requirements\n- **Demo**: https://newtech.dev/auth/sign-in\n- **Roadmap**: https://betterauthui.featurebase.app/roadmap\n\n## Setup Overview\n\nBetter Auth UI provides \"ready-to-use shadcn/ui styled components for rapidly implementing authentication features in your Next.js and React applications.\"\n\n### Key Features\nThe library emphasizes three main benefits:\n1. **Easy** – Plug and play authentication components\n2. **Customizable** – Fully styled with TailwindCSS and shadcn/ui\n3. **Robust** – Built with modern best practices for React projects\n\n### Before Installation\n\nThe documentation recommends reviewing the **Requirements** page before starting installation to ensure seamless integration of the `@daveyplate/better-auth-ui` library.\n\n### Available Integration Paths\n\nThe documentation covers setup for:\n- Next.js\n- TanStack Start\n- React\n\n## Additional Resources\n\n- **LLMs.txt file**: https://better-auth-ui.com/llms.txt (helps AI understand the auth UI)\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/daveyplate/better-auth-ui\n- **Creator**: @daveycodez","durationMs":5319,"url":"https://better-auth-ui.com"}}
