\n    80→          <ClerkSignUpForm\n    81→            initialValues={{\n    82→              emailAddress: 'your_mail+clerk_test@example.com'\n    83→            }}\n    84→          />\n    85→          <div className='text-muted-foreground space-y-2 px-8 text-center text-xs'>\n    86→            <p>\n    87→              This is an{' '}\n    88→              <Link href='/about' className='hover:text-primary underline underline-offset-4'>\n    89→                open-source project\n    90→              </Link>{' '}\n    91→              for demo purposes. Authentication is handled securely by Clerk.\n    92→            </p>\n    93→            <p>\n    94→              <Link\n    95→                href='https://github.com/kiranism/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter'\n    96→                target='_blank'\n    97→                className='hover:text-primary underline underline-offset-4'\n    98→              >\n    99→                View on GitHub\n   100→              </Link>\n   101→            </p>\n   102→          </div>\n   103→          <p className='text-muted-foreground px-8 text-center text-sm'>\n   104→            By clicking continue, you agree to our{' '}\n   105→            <Link\n   106→              href='/terms-of-service'\n   107→              className='hover:text-primary underline underline-offset-4'\n   108→            >\n   109→              Terms of Service\n   110→            </Link>{' '}\n   111→            and{' '}\n   112→            <Link\n   113→              href='/privacy-policy'\n   114→              className='hover:text-primary underline underline-offset-4'\n   115→            >\n   116→              Privacy Policy\n   117→            </Link>\n   118→            .\n   119→          </p>\n   120→        </div>\n   121→      </div>\n   122→    </div>\n   123→  );\n   124→}\n   125→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01AGzBvQkycU8KLSciqMzzAB","session_id":"a376da1e-a7ce-441b-9f5b-3e1afd8c1168","uuid":"c73d1c22-e07c-4cbc-b518-5b2e69003af