{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AGzBvQkycU8KLSciqMzzAB","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me create a comprehensive summary of my findings:\n\n## Auth Pages and Components Summary\n\nI've completed a thorough search of your Next.js project. Here's what I found:\n\n### 1. **Clerk Sign-In/Sign-Up Pages (Catch-all Routes)**\n\nLocated at the expected paths:\n- **Sign-In Route**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/auth/sign-in/[[...sign-in]]/page.tsx`\n- **Sign-Up Route**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/auth/sign-up/[[...sign-up]]/page.tsx`\n\nBoth use Clerk's pre-built components:\n- Sign-in uses `<ClerkSignInForm />` from `@clerk/nextjs`\n- Sign-up uses `<ClerkSignUpForm />` from `@clerk/nextjs`\n\n### 2. **Auth Layout & Root Page**\n\n- **Layout**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/auth/layout.tsx` - Minimal layout that just disables robots indexing and renders children\n- **Root Auth Page**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/auth/page.tsx` - Redirects to `/auth/sign-in`\n\n### 3. **Auth Components in features/auth/**\n\nLocated at `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/features/auth/components/`:\n- `sign-in-view.tsx` - Renders Clerk's SignIn form with GitHub stars counter and interactive grid background\n- `sign-up-view.tsx` - Renders Clerk's SignUp form with GitHub stars counter and interactive grid background\n- `user-auth-form.tsx` - Custom form using TanStack Form + Zod (email validation example, currently unused in main auth flow)\n- `github-auth-button.tsx` - Button component for GitHub OAuth (currently a stub)\n- `interactive-grid.tsx` - Visual grid pattern component for auth page backgrounds\n\n### 4. **AuthUIProvider Setup**\n\nLocated at `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/components/layout/providers.tsx`:\n\nUses `@daveyplate/better-auth-ui` with:\n- `AuthUIProvider` wrapping the app\n- `authClient` from `@/lib/auth-client`\n- Router callbacks for navigation and session changes\n- `ActiveThemeProvider` for theme management\n- `QueryProvider` (React Query) for data fetching\n\n### 5. **Better Auth Server Setup**\n\n- **Server Auth**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/lib/auth.ts`\n  - Uses `better-auth` v1.5.6 with Drizzle + SQLite adapter\n  - Enables email/password authentication\n  - Uses `nextCookies()` plugin for Next.js\n\n- **Client Auth**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/lib/auth-client.ts`\n  - Simple `createAuthClient()` from `better-auth/react`\n\n- **Database Schema**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/lib/auth-schema.ts`\n  - Tables: `user`, `session`, `account`, `verification`\n  - Uses Drizzle ORM with SQLite\n\n### 6. **API Route**\n\n- **Auth API Handler**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/api/auth/[...all]/route.ts`\n  - Catch-all route using `toNextJsHandler(auth)` from better-auth\n  - Handles both POST and GET requests\n\n### 7. **Middleware**\n\n**No middleware.ts file exists** at the project root level. The project does not have auth-specific middleware configured yet.\n\n### 8. **Key Dependencies**\n\nFrom package.json:\n- `@clerk/nextjs`: ^6.39.1\n- `@daveyplate/better-auth-ui`: ^3.4.0\n- `better-auth`: ^1.5.6\n- `@tanstack/react-query`: ^5.95.2\n\n### Current Architecture\n\nThe project has a **dual-auth setup**:\n1. **Clerk** - Used for the public-facing sign-in/sign-up pages\n2. **Better Auth** - Set up on the backend with SQLite database but components not fully integrated into the UI yet\n\nThe auth pages currently use Clerk's pre-built forms, while the Better Auth infrastructure is in place for future integration via the `better-auth-ui` provider."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a42d5759665da1446 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 66115\ntool_uses: 27\nduration_ms: 35275</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a376da1e-a7ce-441b-9f5b-3e1afd8c1168","uuid":"4b8502ac-e0b0-4fc5-87e0-2cd1370536e1","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Find all files related to auth pages, sign-in, sign-up in this Next.js project. I need to understand:\n1. Current Clerk sign-in/sign-up page locations (look for [[...sign-in]], [[...sign-up]] catch-all routes)\n2. Any auth components in src/features/auth/\n3. The current providers.tsx to see AuthUIProvider setup\n4. Any existing app/auth/ directory\n5. The current middleware.ts if it exists\n\nSearch thoroughly in src/app/ for any sign-in, sign-up related routes. Also check src/features/auth/.","agentId":"a42d5759665da1446","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me create a comprehensive summary of my findings:\n\n## Auth Pages and Components Summary\n\nI've completed a thorough search of your Next.js project. Here's what I found:\n\n### 1. **Clerk Sign-In/Sign-Up Pages (Catch-all Routes)**\n\nLocated at the expected paths:\n- **Sign-In Route**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/auth/sign-in/[[...sign-in]]/page.tsx`\n- **Sign-Up Route**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/auth/sign-up/[[...sign-up]]/page.tsx`\n\nBoth use Clerk's pre-built components:\n- Sign-in uses `<ClerkSignInForm />` from `@clerk/nextjs`\n- Sign-up uses `<ClerkSignUpForm />` from `@clerk/nextjs`\n\n### 2. **Auth Layout & Root Page**\n\n- **Layout**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/auth/layout.tsx` - Minimal layout that just disables robots indexing and renders children\n- **Root Auth Page**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/auth/page.tsx` - Redirects to `/auth/sign-in`\n\n### 3. **Auth Components in features/auth/**\n\nLocated at `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/features/auth/components/`:\n- `sign-in-view.tsx` - Renders Clerk's SignIn form with GitHub stars counter and interactive grid background\n- `sign-up-view.tsx` - Renders Clerk's SignUp form with GitHub stars counter and interactive grid background\n- `user-auth-form.tsx` - Custom form using TanStack Form + Zod (email validation example, currently unused in main auth flow)\n- `github-auth-button.tsx` - Button component for GitHub OAuth (currently a stub)\n- `interactive-grid.tsx` - Visual grid pattern component for auth page backgrounds\n\n### 4. **AuthUIProvider Setup**\n\nLocated at `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/components/layout/providers.tsx`:\n\nUses `@daveyplate/better-auth-ui` with:\n- `AuthUIProvider` wrapping the app\n- `authClient` from `@/lib/auth-client`\n- Router callbacks for navigation and session changes\n- `ActiveThemeProvider` for theme management\n- `QueryProvider` (React Query) for data fetching\n\n### 5. **Better Auth Server Setup**\n\n- **Server Auth**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/lib/auth.ts`\n  - Uses `better-auth` v1.5.6 with Drizzle + SQLite adapter\n  - Enables email/password authentication\n  - Uses `nextCookies()` plugin for Next.js\n\n- **Client Auth**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/lib/auth-client.ts`\n  - Simple `createAuthClient()` from `better-auth/react`\n\n- **Database Schema**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/lib/auth-schema.ts`\n  - Tables: `user`, `session`, `account`, `verification`\n  - Uses Drizzle ORM with SQLite\n\n### 6. **API Route**\n\n- **Auth API Handler**: `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/api/auth/[...all]/route.ts`\n  - Catch-all route using `toNextJsHandler(auth)` from better-auth\n  - Handles both POST and GET requests\n\n### 7. **Middleware**\n\n**No middleware.ts file exists** at the project root level. The project does not have auth-specific middleware configured yet.\n\n### 8. **Key Dependencies**\n\nFrom package.json:\n- `@clerk/nextjs`: ^6.39.1\n- `@daveyplate/better-auth-ui`: ^3.4.0\n- `better-auth`: ^1.5.6\n- `@tanstack/react-query`: ^5.95.2\n\n### Current Architecture\n\nThe project has a **dual-auth setup**:\n1. **Clerk** - Used for the public-facing sign-in/sign-up pages\n2. **Better Auth** - Set up on the backend with SQLite database but components not fully integrated into the UI yet\n\nThe auth pages currently use Clerk's pre-built forms, while the Better Auth infrastructure is in place for future integration via the `better-auth-ui` provider."}],"totalDurationMs":35275,"totalTokens":66115,"totalToolUseCount":27,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2095,"cache_read_input_tokens":62781,"output_tokens":1232,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2095},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
