{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TVne7Duq7hh6pcfnrnWFhK","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→'use client';\n     2→import { AuthUIProvider } from '@daveyplate/better-auth-ui';\n     3→import Link from 'next/link';\n     4→import { useRouter } from 'next/navigation';\n     5→import React from 'react';\n     6→import { authClient } from '@/lib/auth-client';\n     7→import { ActiveThemeProvider } from '../themes/active-theme';\n     8→import QueryProvider from './query-provider';\n     9→\n    10→export default function Providers({\n    11→  activeThemeValue,\n    12→  children\n    13→}: {\n    14→  activeThemeValue: string;\n    15→  children: React.ReactNode;\n    16→}) {\n    17→  const router = useRouter();\n    18→\n    19→  return (\n    20→    <>\n    21→      <ActiveThemeProvider initialTheme={activeThemeValue}>\n    22→        <AuthUIProvider\n    23→          authClient={authClient}\n    24→          navigate={router.push}\n    25→          replace={router.replace}\n    26→          onSessionChange={() => {\n    27→            router.refresh();\n    28→          }}\n    29→          Link={Link}\n    30→        >\n    31→          <QueryProvider>{children}</QueryProvider>\n    32→        </AuthUIProvider>\n    33→      </ActiveThemeProvider>\n    34→    </>\n    35→  );\n    36→}\n    37→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a376da1e-a7ce-441b-9f5b-3e1afd8c1168","uuid":"5995dc24-fefc-4ac2-81e4-d83ede36253c","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/components/layout/providers.tsx","content":"'use client';\nimport { AuthUIProvider } from '@daveyplate/better-auth-ui';\nimport Link from 'next/link';\nimport { useRouter } from 'next/navigation';\nimport React from 'react';\nimport { authClient } from '@/lib/auth-client';\nimport { ActiveThemeProvider } from '../themes/active-theme';\nimport QueryProvider from './query-provider';\n\nexport default function Providers({\n  activeThemeValue,\n  children\n}: {\n  activeThemeValue: string;\n  children: React.ReactNode;\n}) {\n  const router = useRouter();\n\n  return (\n    <>\n      <ActiveThemeProvider initialTheme={activeThemeValue}>\n        <AuthUIProvider\n          authClient={authClient}\n          navigate={router.push}\n          replace={router.replace}\n          onSessionChange={() => {\n            router.refresh();\n          }}\n          Link={Link}\n        >\n          <QueryProvider>{children}</QueryProvider>\n        </AuthUIProvider>\n      </ActiveThemeProvider>\n    </>\n  );\n}\n","numLines":37,"startLine":1,"totalLines":37}}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_016w9PZM8TLqMmm3mHT2wLid","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to:\n1. Create `src/app/auth/[path]/page.tsx` with `<AuthView />` from better-auth-ui\n2. Remove the old Clerk catch-all routes (`sign-in/[[...sign-in]]` and `sign-up/[[...sign-up]]`)\n3. Remove or update the Clerk auth components in `src/features/auth/components/`\n4. Update the auth root page to redirect to /auth/sign-in\n5. Keep the auth layout\n\nLet me check better-auth-ui docs for the correct AuthView usage. From the progress notes: \"Auth routes use `<AuthView path={path} />` from `@daveyplate/better-auth-ui` with dynamic `[path]` param\" and \"Static params generated via `authViewPaths` from `@daveyplate/better-auth-ui/server`\"\n\n\nI also need to set up the post-sign-in redirect to point to /dashboard/overview through the AuthUIProvider configuration, then build out the dynamic auth route and remove the old Clerk routes.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":536,"cache_read_input_tokens":31584,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":536},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a376da1e-a7ce-441b-9f5b-3e1afd8c1168","uuid":"4696c383-a4f2-4dec-99b3-61b9f695a457"}
