{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012AYM88bgfuoCZ1JjESewAn","type":"tool_result","content":"# Next.js App Router Auth Setup Guide\n\n## 1) Dynamic Auth Route File\n\nCreate `app/auth/[path]/page.tsx`:\n\n```typescript\nimport { AuthView } from \"@daveyplate/better-auth-ui\"\nimport { authViewPaths } from \"@daveyplate/better-auth-ui/server\"\n\nexport const dynamicParams = false\n\nexport function generateStaticParams() {\n    return Object.values(authViewPaths).map((path) => ({ path }))\n}\n\nexport default async function AuthPage({ params }: { params: Promise<{ path: string }> }) {\n    const { path } = await params\n    \n    return (\n        <main className=\"container flex grow flex-col items-center justify-center self-center p-4 md:p-6\">\n            <AuthView path={path} />\n        </main>\n    )\n}\n```\n\n## 2) Static Parameters Generation\n\nThe `generateStaticParams()` function uses `authViewPaths` to create static routes for: `/auth/sign-in`, `/auth/sign-up`, `/auth/magic-link`, `/auth/forgot-password`, `/auth/two-factor`, `/auth/recover-account`, `/auth/reset-password`, `/auth/sign-out`, `/auth/callback`, and `/auth/accept-invitation`.\n\n## 3) Post-Sign-In Redirect Configuration\n\nPass a redirect URL through `AuthUIProvider` props in `app/providers.tsx`:\n\n```typescript\n<AuthUIProvider\n    authClient={authClient}\n    navigate={router.push}\n    replace={router.replace}\n    onSessionChange={() => router.refresh()}\n    redirects={{\n        afterSignIn: \"/dashboard/overview\"\n    }}\n    Link={Link}\n>\n```\n\n## 4) AuthUIProvider Core Props\n\nEssential configuration in your providers component:\n\n- `authClient`: Your Better Auth client instance\n- `navigate`: Router push function (`router.push`)\n- `replace`: Router replace function (`router.replace`)\n- `onSessionChange`: Callback executing `router.refresh()` to clear Next.js cache\n- `redirects.afterSignIn`: Target path after authentication succeeds\n- `Link`: Next.js Link component for client navigation"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a376da1e-a7ce-441b-9f5b-3e1afd8c1168","uuid":"79163704-45e2-4d09-9c6c-b9638ff4af28","tool_use_result":{"bytes":463231,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Next.js App Router Auth Setup Guide\n\n## 1) Dynamic Auth Route File\n\nCreate `app/auth/[path]/page.tsx`:\n\n```typescript\nimport { AuthView } from \"@daveyplate/better-auth-ui\"\nimport { authViewPaths } from \"@daveyplate/better-auth-ui/server\"\n\nexport const dynamicParams = false\n\nexport function generateStaticParams() {\n    return Object.values(authViewPaths).map((path) => ({ path }))\n}\n\nexport default async function AuthPage({ params }: { params: Promise<{ path: string }> }) {\n    const { path } = await params\n    \n    return (\n        <main className=\"container flex grow flex-col items-center justify-center self-center p-4 md:p-6\">\n            <AuthView path={path} />\n        </main>\n    )\n}\n```\n\n## 2) Static Parameters Generation\n\nThe `generateStaticParams()` function uses `authViewPaths` to create static routes for: `/auth/sign-in`, `/auth/sign-up`, `/auth/magic-link`, `/auth/forgot-password`, `/auth/two-factor`, `/auth/recover-account`, `/auth/reset-password`, `/auth/sign-out`, `/auth/callback`, and `/auth/accept-invitation`.\n\n## 3) Post-Sign-In Redirect Configuration\n\nPass a redirect URL through `AuthUIProvider` props in `app/providers.tsx`:\n\n```typescript\n<AuthUIProvider\n    authClient={authClient}\n    navigate={router.push}\n    replace={router.replace}\n    onSessionChange={() => router.refresh()}\n    redirects={{\n        afterSignIn: \"/dashboard/overview\"\n    }}\n    Link={Link}\n>\n```\n\n## 4) AuthUIProvider Core Props\n\nEssential configuration in your providers component:\n\n- `authClient`: Your Better Auth client instance\n- `navigate`: Router push function (`router.push`)\n- `replace`: Router replace function (`router.replace`)\n- `onSessionChange`: Callback executing `router.refresh()` to clear Next.js cache\n- `redirects.afterSignIn`: Target path after authentication succeeds\n- `Link`: Next.js Link component for client navigation","durationMs":5936,"url":"https://better-auth-ui.com/integrations/next-js"}}
