{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0162RUw3p8h4hfwnhBUqGwTM","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have a comprehensive view. Let me compile the complete report.\n\n## Summary: Organization, Org-Switcher, and Workspace Files\n\nI've conducted a thorough search of the codebase. Here are all the files related to organizations, org-switcher, and workspaces:\n\n### **Core Organization Files**\n\n1. **Organization Switcher Component**\n   - `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/components/org-switcher.tsx`\n     - Uses `@clerk/nextjs` hooks: `useAuth()`, `useOrganizationList()`\n     - Implements dropdown menu for switching between organizations\n     - Displays active organization with logo/image\n     - Routes to `/dashboard/workspaces` for creating new organizations\n\n2. **Authentication Files**\n   - `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/lib/auth.ts` - Better Auth server-side setup\n   - `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/lib/auth-client.ts` - Better Auth client-side setup\n\n### **Workspace Pages**\n\n1. **Workspaces List Page**\n   - `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/dashboard/workspaces/page.tsx`\n     - Uses Clerk's `OrganizationList` component\n     - Styled with custom appearance config\n     - Redirects to `/dashboard/workspaces/team` after selection/creation\n\n2. **Team Management Page**\n   - `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/dashboard/workspaces/team/[[...rest]]/page.tsx`\n     - Uses Clerk's `OrganizationProfile` component\n     - Manages team members, roles, security, and organization settings\n\n### **Configuration Files**\n\n1. **Navigation Configuration**\n   - `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/config/nav-config.ts`\n     - Defines navigation structure with RBAC support\n     - Includes workspace and teams menu items\n     - \"Workspaces\" item: `/dashboard/workspaces` (no access control)\n     - \"Teams\" item: `/dashboard/workspaces/team` (requires `requireOrg: true`)\n     - \"Billing\" item: requires `requireOrg: true`\n\n2. **Info Content Configuration**\n   - `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/config/infoconfig.ts`\n     - `workspacesInfoContent` - Help text for workspaces page\n     - `teamInfoContent` - Help text for team management page\n     - Links to Clerk Organizations documentation\n\n### **Layout & Integration**\n\n1. **App Sidebar Component**\n   - `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/components/layout/app-sidebar.tsx`\n     - Imports and renders `<OrgSwitcher />` in the SidebarHeader\n     - Uses `authClient` from `@/lib/auth-client` for session management\n     - Uses `useFilteredNavGroups()` for RBAC navigation filtering\n\n2. **Dashboard Layout**\n   - `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/dashboard/layout.tsx`\n     - Provides SidebarProvider, InfobarProvider, and AppSidebar to all dashboard pages\n\n3. **Root Providers**\n   - `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/components/layout/providers.tsx`\n     - Wraps app with `AuthUIProvider` from `@daveyplate/better-auth-ui`\n     - Uses `authClient` for session management\n\n### **RBAC/Access Control**\n\n1. **Navigation RBAC Hook**\n   - `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/hooks/use-nav.ts`\n     - Uses Clerk hooks: `useOrganization()`, `useUser()`\n     - Fully client-side filtering based on:\n       - `requireOrg` - requires active organization\n       - `permission` - requires specific Clerk permission\n       - `role` - requires specific Clerk role\n     - Recursively filters navigation items and groups\n\n2. **Type Definitions**\n   - `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/types/index.ts`\n     - `PermissionCheck` interface defines access control properties\n     - `NavItem`, `NavGroup` interfaces support `access?: PermissionCheck`\n\n### **Clerk Integration**\n\n**Library Version**: `@clerk/nextjs@^6.39.1` (in package.json)\n\n**Clerk Imports Used**:\n- `useAuth()` - Gets current auth context (`orgId`, `userId`)\n- `useOrganizationList()` - Lists user's organization memberships\n- `useOrganization()` - Gets current organization context\n- `useUser()` - Gets current user\n- `OrganizationList` component - Manages organization selection/creation\n- `OrganizationProfile` component - Full organization/team management UI\n\n**Key Note**: The codebase uses **Clerk Organizations** for workspace management, NOT Clerk's deprecated `OrganizationSwitcher` component. Instead, it implements a custom org-switcher using Clerk's hooks.\n\n### **Environment Variables** (from env.example.txt)\n\n```\nNEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=       # Clerk API key\nCLERK_SECRET_KEY=                         # Clerk secret\nNEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_IN_URL=/auth/sign-in\nNEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_UP_URL=/auth/sign-up\nNEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_IN_URL=/dashboard/overview\nNEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_AFTER_SIGN_UP_URL=/dashboard/overview\nWEBHOOK_SECRET=                           # Optional for production webhooks\n```"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a54dc8422ba501d10 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 75103\ntool_uses: 34\nduration_ms: 40728</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5831c654-5660-41f9-8789-6e410bfc3f8c","uuid":"2057d892-63d7-44b5-9bd8-f26482a091cc","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Find all files related to organizations, org-switcher, workspaces in the codebase. Also find the current auth.ts, auth-c