{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01U9mV7EKAh3moYm9WgjTapp","type":"tool_result","content":"# Better Auth Organization Plugin Setup\n\n## Server-Side Setup\n\n```typescript\nimport { betterAuth } from \"better-auth\"\nimport { organization } from \"better-auth/plugins\"\n\nexport const auth = betterAuth({\n  plugins: [\n    organization({\n      allowUserToCreateOrganization: true,\n      creatorRole: \"owner\",\n      membershipLimit: 100,\n      async sendInvitationEmail(data) {\n        // Email implementation\n      }\n    })\n  ]\n})\n```\n\n## Client-Side Setup\n\n```typescript\nimport { createAuthClient } from \"better-auth/client\"\nimport { organizationClient } from \"better-auth/client/plugins\"\n\nexport const authClient = createAuthClient({\n  plugins: [organizationClient()]\n})\n```\n\n## Database Tables Created\n\n- **organization**: stores org details (name, slug, logo, metadata)\n- **member**: tracks users and their roles within organizations\n- **invitation**: manages pending member invitations\n- **session**: extended with `activeOrganizationId` and `activeTeamId` fields\n- **organizationRole** (optional): for dynamic role management\n- **team** & **teamMember** (optional): when teams feature enabled\n\n## Core API Methods\n\n| Operation | Client | Server |\n|-----------|--------|--------|\n| Create org | `organization.create()` | `auth.api.createOrganization()` |\n| List orgs | `organization.list()` | `auth.api.listOrganizations()` |\n| Set active | `organization.setActive()` | `auth.api.setActiveOrganization()` |\n| Get active | `useActiveOrganization()` | `auth.api.getActiveMember()` |\n| Invite member | `organization.inviteMember()` | `auth.api.createInvitation()` |\n| Accept invite | `organization.acceptInvitation()` | `auth.api.acceptInvitation()` |\n| List members | `organization.listMembers()` | `auth.api.listMembers()` |\n| Update role | `organization.updateMemberRole()` | `auth.api.updateMemberRole()` |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5831c654-5660-41f9-8789-6e410bfc3f8c","uuid":"c57b93b1-9a4a-47b4-b2a8-1a8a10649e35","tool_use_result":{"bytes":2339544,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Better Auth Organization Plugin Setup\n\n## Server-Side Setup\n\n```typescript\nimport { betterAuth } from \"better-auth\"\nimport { organization } from \"better-auth/plugins\"\n\nexport const auth = betterAuth({\n  plugins: [\n    organization({\n      allowUserToCreateOrganization: true,\n      creatorRole: \"owner\",\n      membershipLimit: 100,\n      async sendInvitationEmail(data) {\n        // Email implementation\n      }\n    })\n  ]\n})\n```\n\n## Client-Side Setup\n\n```typescript\nimport { createAuthClient } from \"better-auth/client\"\nimport { organizationClient } from \"better-auth/client/plugins\"\n\nexport const authClient = createAuthClient({\n  plugins: [organizationClient()]\n})\n```\n\n## Database Tables Created\n\n- **organization**: stores org details (name, slug, logo, metadata)\n- **member**: tracks users and their roles within organizations\n- **invitation**: manages pending member invitations\n- **session**: extended with `activeOrganizationId` and `activeTeamId` fields\n- **organizationRole** (optional): for dynamic role management\n- **team** & **teamMember** (optional): when teams feature enabled\n\n## Core API Methods\n\n| Operation | Client | Server |\n|-----------|--------|--------|\n| Create org | `organization.create()` | `auth.api.createOrganization()` |\n| List orgs | `organization.list()` | `auth.api.listOrganizations()` |\n| Set active | `organization.setActive()` | `auth.api.setActiveOrganization()` |\n| Get active | `useActiveOrganization()` | `auth.api.getActiveMember()` |\n| Invite member | `organization.inviteMember()` | `auth.api.createInvitation()` |\n| Accept invite | `organization.acceptInvitation()` | `auth.api.acceptInvitation()` |\n| List members | `organization.listMembers()` | `auth.api.listMembers()` |\n| Update role | `organization.updateMemberRole()` | `auth.api.updateMemberRole()` |","durationMs":6740,"url":"https://www.better-auth.com/docs/plugins/organization"}}
