{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018xMnnHGf13aJkwLCYvuH4h","type":"tool_result","content":"# Better Auth UI - Components & Navigation Structure\n\n## Organization-Related Components\n\nThe documentation includes these organization management components:\n\n- **`<OrganizationSwitcher />`** - Enables users to switch between organizations\n- **`<OrganizationSettingsCards />`** - \"A collection of organization management cards for settings\"\n- **`<OrganizationMembersCard />`** - Displays and manages organization member lists\n- **`<AcceptInvitationCard />`** - Handles organization invitation acceptance\n\n## Complete Navigation Structure\n\n### Top-Level Sections\n1. **Introduction** - Overview and feature highlights\n2. **Getting Started** - Requirements and Installation guides\n3. **Integrations** - Next.js, TanStack Start, React\n4. **Data** - TanStack Query, Triplit, InstantDB\n5. **Components** - Full UI component library\n6. **Advanced** - Organizations, API Keys, Localization, custom configurations\n7. **API Reference** - TypeScript interfaces and hooks\n\n### Components Category Breakdown\n- Auth components (`<AuthView />`, `<AuthUIProvider />`)\n- User management (`<UserAvatar />`, `<UserButton />`)\n- Organization tools (switcher, settings, members, invitations)\n- Account settings (email, password, avatar, username, name)\n- Security features (sessions, two-factor, passkeys, providers)\n- Conditional rendering (`<SignedIn />`, `<SignedOut />`, `<AuthLoading />`)\n- Email templates\n- Redirect utilities"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5831c654-5660-41f9-8789-6e410bfc3f8c","uuid":"b2cc55a9-29f8-462f-b4b7-e3fab40049cb","tool_use_result":{"bytes":134836,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Better Auth UI - Components & Navigation Structure\n\n## Organization-Related Components\n\nThe documentation includes these organization management components:\n\n- **`<OrganizationSwitcher />`** - Enables users to switch between organizations\n- **`<OrganizationSettingsCards />`** - \"A collection of organization management cards for settings\"\n- **`<OrganizationMembersCard />`** - Displays and manages organization member lists\n- **`<AcceptInvitationCard />`** - Handles organization invitation acceptance\n\n## Complete Navigation Structure\n\n### Top-Level Sections\n1. **Introduction** - Overview and feature highlights\n2. **Getting Started** - Requirements and Installation guides\n3. **Integrations** - Next.js, TanStack Start, React\n4. **Data** - TanStack Query, Triplit, InstantDB\n5. **Components** - Full UI component library\n6. **Advanced** - Organizations, API Keys, Localization, custom configurations\n7. **API Reference** - TypeScript interfaces and hooks\n\n### Components Category Breakdown\n- Auth components (`<AuthView />`, `<AuthUIProvider />`)\n- User management (`<UserAvatar />`, `<UserButton />`)\n- Organization tools (switcher, settings, members, invitations)\n- Account settings (email, password, avatar, username, name)\n- Security features (sessions, two-factor, passkeys, providers)\n- Conditional rendering (`<SignedIn />`, `<SignedOut />`, `<AuthLoading />`)\n- Email templates\n- Redirect utilities","durationMs":5677,"url":"https://better-auth-ui.com"}}
