{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01ArkZMjXQQn7qhGSCK9AbSX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_018djMMCpwdg14HysfJyrq4v","name":"WebFetch","input":{"url":"https://www.better-auth.com/docs/plugins/stripe","prompt":"I need to understand:\n1. How to use subscription.list() on the client - what parameters does it take and what does it return?\n2. How to use subscription.upgrade() - what parameters and return values?\n3. Is there a useListSubscriptions hook or similar React hook?\n4. How does the organization subscription work - do you pass referenceId as the org id?\n5. What is the subscription object shape (fields like status, plan, etc)?"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":234,"cache_read_input_tokens":45666,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":234},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5ecfe1e9-6f52-4d05-b142-586fa1064d01","uuid":"052d28c4-8ece-416c-8785-1863bfd28b6a"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018djMMCpwdg14HysfJyrq4v","type":"tool_result","content":"# Better Auth Stripe Subscription API Summary\n\n## subscription.list()\n\n**Client Usage:**\n```typescript\nconst { data: subscriptions, error } = await authClient.subscription.list({\n    query: {\n        referenceId: '123',\n        customerType, // \"user\" | \"organization\"\n    },\n});\n```\n\n**Returns:** An array of subscription objects with fields like `status` (\"active\", \"trialing\", \"canceled\"), `plan`, `limits`, `periodStart`, `periodEnd`, `seats`, and `strialStart`/`trialEnd`.\n\n## subscription.upgrade()\n\n**Client Usage:**\n```typescript\nconst { data, error } = await authClient.subscription.upgrade({\n    plan: \"pro\",           // required\n    successUrl: \"/dash\",   // required\n    cancelUrl: \"/pricing\", // required\n    annual: true,          // optional\n    referenceId: \"123\",    // optional, defaults by customerType\n    subscriptionId: \"sub_123\", // pass when upgrading existing\n    seats: 5,              // optional, for team plans\n    locale: \"en\",          // optional\n    disableRedirect: false,\n    scheduleAtPeriodEnd: false,\n});\n```\n\n## Organization Subscriptions\n\nAccording to the documentation, organizations act as the billing entity when `customerType: \"organization\"` is specified. \"The referenceId parameter represents the entity being billed—typically a user ID by default, or an organization ID when using organization-based billing.\"\n\n## Authorization\n\nAccess requires implementing `authorizeReference` to verify users have permission to manage subscriptions for a given reference ID, particularly for organizations."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5ecfe1e9-6f52-4d05-b142-586fa1064d01","uuid":"9cce33a0-d86e-471a-b4f3-2256668fd6fd","tool_use_result":{"bytes":942420,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Better Auth Stripe Subscription API Summary\n\n## subscription.list()\n\n**Client Usage:**\n```typescript\nconst { data: subscriptions, error } = await authClient.subscription.list({\n    query: {\n        referenceId: '123',\n        customerType, // \"user\" | \"organization\"\n    },\n});\n```\n\n**Returns:** An array of subscription objects with fields like `status` (\"active\", \"trialing\", \"canceled\"), `plan`, `limits`, `periodStart`, `periodEnd`, `seats`, and `strialStart`/`trialEnd`.\n\n## subscription.upgrade()\n\n**Client Usage:**\n```typescript\nconst { data, error } = await authClient.subscription.upgrade({\n    plan: \"pro\",           // required\n    successUrl: \"/dash\",   // required\n    cancelUrl: \"/pricing\", // required\n    annual: true,          // optional\n    referenceId: \"123\",    // optional, defaults by customerType\n    subscriptionId: \"sub_123\", // pass when upgrading existing\n    seats: 5,              // optional, for team plans\n    locale: \"en\",          // optional\n    disableRedirect: false,\n    scheduleAtPeriodEnd: false,\n});\n```\n\n## Organization Subscriptions\n\nAccording to the documentation, organizations act as the billing entity when `customerType: \"organization\"` is specified. \"The referenceId parameter represents the entity being billed—typically a user ID by default, or an organization ID when using organization-based billing.\"\n\n## Authorization\n\nAccess requires implementing `authorizeReference` to verify users have permission to manage subscriptions for a given reference ID, particularly for organizations.","durationMs":5617,"url":"https://www.better-auth.com/docs/plugins/stripe"}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_014tcG2DZrby7umy9376JaHk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me build the billing page. I'll replace the Clerk-based one with a custom shadcn UI."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":704,"cache_read_input_tokens":45900,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":704},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5ecfe1e9-6f52-4d05-b142-586fa1064d01","uuid":"6b677678-fa57-480f-9c8a-a5e30df4762c"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_014tcG2DZrby7umy9376JaHk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01DcZyeZfUc3r9PYRkKwyMwD","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/dashboard/billing/page.tsx","content":"'use client';\n\nimport { useCallback, useEffect, useState } from 'react';\nimport PageContainer from '@/components/layout/page-container';\nimport {\n  Card,\n  CardContent,\n  CardDescription,\n  CardFooter,\n  CardHeader,\n  CardTitle\n} from '@/components/ui/card';\nimport { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';\nimport { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';\nimport { Alert, AlertDescription } from '@/components/ui/alert';\nimport { Icons } from '@/components/icons';\nimport { authClient } from '@/lib/auth-client';\nimport { billingInfoContent } from '@/config/infoconfig';\n\ntype Subscription = {\n  id: string;\n  plan: string;\n  status: string;\n  periodStart?: Date;\n  periodEnd?: Date;\n  seats?: number;\n};\n\nconst plans = [\n  {\n    name: 'free',\n    label: 'Free',\n    description: 'For small teams getting started',\n    features: ['Up to 3 projects', 'Up to 5 members', 'Community support'],\n    price: '$0',\n    period: '/month'\n  },\n  {\n    name: 'pro',\n    label: 'Pro',\n    description: 'For growing teams that need more',\n    features: [\n      'Up to 100 projects',\n      'Up to 50 members',\n      'Priority support',\n      'Exclusive features'\n    ],\n    price: '$19',\n    period: '/month',\n    popular: true\n  }\n];\n\nexport default function BillingPage() {\n  const { data: activeOrg, isPending: orgPending } =\n    authClient.useActiveOrganization();\n  const [subscriptions, setSubscriptions] = useState<Subscription[]>([]);\n  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);\n  const [actionLoading, setActionLoading] = useState<string | null>(null);\n\n  const fetchSubscriptions = useCallback(async () => {\n    if (!activeOrg) return;\n    setLoading(true);\n    try {\n      const { data } = await authClient.subscription.list({\n        query: {\n          referenceId: activeOrg.id\n        }\n      });\n      setSubscriptions((data as Subscription[]) || []);\n    } catch {\n      setSubscriptions([]);\n    } finally {\n      setLoading(false);\n    }\n  }, [activeOrg?.id]);\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    void fetchSubscriptions();\n  }, [fetchSubscriptions]);\n\n  const activeSub = subscriptions.find(\n    (s) => s.status === 'active' || s.status === 'trialing'\n  );\n  const currentPlan = activeSub?.plan || 'free';\n\n  const handleUpgrade = async (planName: string) => {\n    if (!activeOrg) return;\n    setActionLoading(planName);\n    try {\n      await authClient.subscription.upgrade({\n        plan: planName,\n        successUrl: `${window.location.origin}/dashboard/billing`,\n        cancelUrl: `${window.location.origin}/dashboard/billing`,\n        referenceId: activeOrg.id\n      });\n    } finally {\n      setActionLoading(null);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const handleCancel = async () => {\n    if (!activeSub) return;\n    setActionLoading('cancel');\n    try {\n      await authClient.subscription.cancel({\n        subscriptionId: activeSub.id,\n        returnUrl: `${window.location.origin}/dashboard/billing`\n      });\n      await fetchSubscriptions();\n    } finally {\n      setActionLoading(null);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const handlePortal = async () => {\n    setActionLoading('portal');\n    try {\n      await authClient.subscription.billingPortal({\n        returnUrl: `${window.location.origin}/dashboard/billing`\n      });\n    } finally {\n      setActionLoading(null);\n    }\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <PageContainer\n      isLoading={orgPending}\n      access={!!activeOrg}\n      accessFallback={\n        <div className='flex min-h-[400px] items-center justify-center'>\n          <div className='space-y-2 text-center'>\n            <h2 className='text-2xl font-semibold'>No Organization Selected</h2>\n            <p className='text-muted-foreground'>\n              Please select or create an organization to view billing\n              information.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      }\n      infoContent={billingInfoContent}\n      pageTitle='Billing & Plans'\n      pageDescription={`Manage your subscription and usage limits for ${activeOrg?.name}`}\n    >\n      <div className='space-y-6'>\n        <Alert>\n          <Icons.info className='h-4 w-4' />\n          <AlertDescription>\n            Plans and subscriptions are managed through Stripe. Subscribe to a\n            plan to unlock features and higher limits.\n          </AlertDescription>\n        </Alert>\n\n        {/* Current Subscription Status */}\n        {activeSub && (\n          <Card>\n            <CardHeader>\n              <CardTitle className='flex items-center gap-2'>\n                Current Subscription\n                <Badge\n                  variant={\n                    activeSub.status === 'active' ? 'default' : 'secondary'\n                  }\n                >\n                  {activeSub.status}\n                </Badge>\n              </CardTitle>\n              <CardDescription>\n                You are on the{' '}\n                <span className='font-semibold capitalize'>\n                  {activeSub.plan}\n                </span>{' '}\n                plan\n                {activeSub.periodEnd &&\n                  ` · Renews ${new Date(activeSub.periodEnd).toLocaleDateString()}`}\n              </CardDescription>\n            </CardHeader>\n            <CardFooter className='gap-2'>\n              <Button\n                variant='outline'\n                size='sm'\n                onClick={handlePortal}\n                disabled={actionLoading === 'portal'}\n              >\n                {actionLoading === 'portal' && (\n                  <Icons.spinner className='mr-2 h-4 w-4 animate-spin' />\n                )}\n                Manage Billing\n              </Button>\n              {currentPlan !== 'free' && (\n                <Button\n                  variant='outline'\n                  size='sm'\n                  onClick={handleCancel}\n                  disabled={actionLoading === 'cancel'}\n                >\n                  {actionLoading === 'cancel' && (\n                    <Icons.spinner className='mr-2 h-4 w-4 animate-spin' />\n                  )}\n                  Cancel Subscription\n                </Button>\n              )}\n            </CardFooter>\n          </Card>\n        )}\n\n        {/* Plans */}\n        <Card>\n          <CardHeader>\n            <CardTitle>Available Plans</CardTitle>\n            <CardDescription>\n              Choose a plan that fits your organization&apos;s needs\n            </CardDescription>\n          </CardHeader>\n          <CardContent>\n            <div className='mx-auto grid max-w-4xl gap-6 md:grid-cols-2'>\n              {plans.map((plan) => {\n                const isCurrent = currentPlan === plan.name;\n                return (\n                  <Card\n                    key={plan.name}\n                    className={\n                      plan.popular ? 'border-primary shadow-md' : undefined\n                    }\n                  >\n                    <CardHeader>\n                      <div className='flex items-center justify-between'>\n                        <CardTitle className='text-xl'>{plan.label}</CardTitle>\n                        {plan.popular && <Badge>Popular</Badge>}\n                      </div>\n                      <CardDescription>{plan.description}</CardDescription>\n                    </CardHeader>\n                    <CardContent>\n                      <div className='mb-4'>\n                        <span className='text-3xl font-bold'>{plan.price}</span>\n                        <span className='text-muted-foreground'>\n                          {plan.period}\n                        </span>\n                      </div>\n                      <ul className='space-y-2'>\n                        {plan.features.map((feature) => (\n                          <li key={feature} className='flex items-center gap-2'>\n                            <Icons.check className='text-primary h-4 w-4' />\n                            <span className='text-sm'>{feature}</span>\n                          </li>\n                        ))}\n                      </ul>\n                    </CardContent>\n                    <CardFooter>\n                      {isCurrent ? (\n                        <Button className='w-full' disabled variant='outline'>\n                          Current Plan\n                        </Button>\n                      ) : (\n                        <Button\n                          className='w-full'\n                          variant={plan.popular ? 'default' : 'outline'}\n                          disabled={\n                            loading || actionLoading === plan.name\n                          }\n                          onClick={() => handleUpgrade(plan.name)}\n                        >\n                          {actionLoading === plan.name && (\n                            <Icons.spinner className='mr-2 h-4 w-4 animate-spin' />\n                          )}\n                          {plan.name === 'free'\n                            ? 'Downgrade'\n                            : 'Upgrade to Pro'}\n                        </Button>\n                      )}\n                    </CardFooter>\n                  </Card>\n                );\n              })}\n            </div>\n          </CardContent>\n        </Card>\n      </div>\n    </PageContainer>\n  );\n}\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":704,"cache_read_input_tokens":45900,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":704},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5ecfe1e9-6f52-4d05-b142-586fa1064d01","uuid":"63e2bc9c-cc71-4389-bcea-3931842d7288"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DcZyeZfUc3r9PYRkKwyMwD","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/dashboard/billing/page.tsx has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5ecfe1e9-6f52-4d05-b142-586fa1064d01","uuid":"ff629f5b-615f-45dc-9c7a-7f9d5227f69d","tool_use_result":{"type":"update","filePath":"/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/dashboard/billing/page.tsx","content":"'use client';\n\nimport { useCallback, useEffect, useState } from 'react';\nimport PageContainer from '@/components/layout/page-container';\nimport {\n  Card,\n  CardContent,\n  CardDescription,\n  CardFooter,\n  CardHeader,\n  CardTitle\n} from '@/components/ui/card';\nimport { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';\nimport { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';\nimport { Alert, AlertDescription } from '@/components/ui/alert';\nimport { Icons } from '@/components/icons';\nimport { authClient } from '@/lib/auth-client';\nimport { billingInfoContent } from '@/config/infoconfig';\n\ntype Subscription = {\n  id: string;\n  plan: string;\n  status: string;\n  periodStart?: Date;\n  periodEnd?: Date;\n  seats?: number;\n};\n\nconst plans = [\n  {\n    name: 'free',\n    label: 'Free',\n    description: 'For small teams getting started',\n    features: ['Up to 3 projects', 'Up to 5 members', 'Community support'],\n    price: '$0',\n    period: '/month'\n  },\n  {\n    name: 'pro',\n    label: 'Pro',\n    description: 'For growing teams that need more',\n    features: [\n      'Up to 100 projects',\n      'Up to 50 members',\n      'Priority support',\n      'Exclusive features'\n    ],\n    price: '$19',\n    period: '/month',\n    popular: true\n  }\n];\n\nexport default function BillingPage() {\n  const { data: activeOrg, isPending: orgPending } =\n    authClient.useActiveOrganization();\n  const [subscriptions, setSubscriptions] = useState<Subscription[]>([]);\n  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);\n  const [actionLoading, setActionLoading] = useState<string | null>(null);\n\n  const fetchSubscriptions = useCallback(async () => {\n    if (!activeOrg) return;\n    setLoading(true);\n    try {\n      const { data } = await authClient.subscription.list({\n        query: {\n          referenceId: activeOrg.id\n        }\n      });\n      setSubscriptions((data as Subscription[]) || []);\n    } catch {\n      setSubscriptions([]);\n    } finally {\n      setLoading(false);\n    }\n  }, [activeOrg?.id]);\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    void fetchSubscriptions();\n  }, [fetchSubscriptions]);\n\n  const activeSub = subscriptions.find(\n    (s) => s.status === 'active' || s.status === 'trialing'\n  );\n  const currentPlan = activeSub?.plan || 'free';\n\n  const handleUpgrade = async (planName: string) => {\n    if (!activeOrg) return;\n    setActionLoading(planName);\n    try {\n      await authClient.subscription.upgrade({\n        plan: planName,\n        successUrl: `${window.location.origin}/dashboard/billing`,\n        cancelUrl: `${window.location.origin}/dashboard/billing`,\n        referenceId: activeOrg.id\n      });\n    } finally {\n      setActionLoading(null);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const handleCancel = async () => {\n    if (!activeSub) return;\n    setActionLoading('cancel');\n    try {\n      await authClient.subscription.cancel({\n        subscriptionId: activeSub.id,\n        returnUrl: `${window.location.origin}/dashboard/billing`\n      });\n      await fetchSubscriptions();\n    } finally {\n      setActionLoading(null);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const handlePortal = async () => {\n    setActionLoading('portal');\n    try {\n      await authClient.subscription.billingPortal({\n        returnUrl: `${window.location.origin}/dashboard/billing`\n      });\n    } finally {\n      setActionLoading(null);\n    }\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <PageContainer\n      isLoading={orgPending}\n      access={!!activeOrg}\n      accessFallback={\n        <div className='flex min-h-[400px] items-center justify-center'>\n          <div className='space-y-2 text-center'>\n            <h2 className='text-2xl font-semibold'>No Organization Selected</h2>\n            <p className='text-muted-foreground'>\n              Please select or create an organization to view billing\n              information.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      }\n      infoContent={billingInfoContent}\n      pageTitle='Billing & Plans'\n      pageDescription={`Manage your subscription and usage limits for ${activeOrg?.name}`}\n    >\n      <div className='space-y-6'>\n        <Alert>\n          <Icons.info className='h-4 w-4' />\n          <AlertDescription>\n            Plans and subscriptions are managed through Stripe. Subscribe to a\n            plan to unlock features and higher limits.\n          </AlertDescription>\n        </Alert>\n\n        {/* Current Subscription Status */}\n        {activeSub && (\n          <Card>\n            <CardHeader>\n              <CardTitle className='flex items-center gap-2'>\n                Current Subscription\n                <Badge\n                  variant={\n                    activeSub.status === 'active' ? 'default' : 'secondary'\n                  }\n                >\n                  {activeSub.status}\n                </Badge>\n              </CardTitle>\n              <CardDescription>\n                You are on the{' '}\n                <span className='font-semibold capitalize'>\n                  {activeSub.plan}\n                </span>{' '}\n                plan\n                {activeSub.periodEnd &&\n                  ` · Renews ${new Date(activeSub.periodEnd).toLocaleDateString()}`}\n              </CardDescription>\n            </CardHeader>\n            <CardFooter className='gap-2'>\n              <Button\n                variant='outline'\n                size='sm'\n                onClick={handlePortal}\n                disabled={actionLoading === 'portal'}\n              >\n                {actionLoading === 'portal' && (\n                  <Icons.spinner className='mr-2 h-4 w-4 animate-spin' />\n                )}\n                Manage Billing\n              </Button>\n              {currentPlan !== 'free' && (\n                <Button\n                  variant='outline'\n                  size='sm'\n                  onClick={handleCancel}\n                  disabled={actionLoading === 'cancel'}\n                >\n                  {actionLoading === 'cancel' && (\n                    <Icons.spinner className='mr-2 h-4 w-4 animate-spin' />\n                  )}\n                  Cancel Subscription\n                </Button>\n              )}\n            </CardFooter>\n          </Card>\n        )}\n\n        {/* Plans */}\n        <Card>\n          <CardHeader>\n            <CardTitle>Available Plans</CardTitle>\n            <CardDescription>\n              Choose a plan that fits your organization&apos;s needs\n            </CardDescription>\n          </CardHeader>\n          <CardContent>\n            <div className='mx-auto grid max-w-4xl gap-6 md:grid-cols-2'>\n              {plans.map((plan) => {\n                const isCurrent = currentPlan === plan.name;\n                return (\n                  <Card\n                    key={plan.name}\n                    className={\n                      plan.popular ? 'border-primary shadow-md' : undefined\n                    }\n                  >\n                    <CardHeader>\n                      <div className='flex items-center justify-between'>\n                        <CardTitle className='text-xl'>{plan.label}</CardTitle>\n                        {plan.popular && <Badge>Popular</Badge>}\n                      </div>\n                      <CardDescription>{plan.description}</CardDescription>\n                    </CardHeader>\n                    <CardContent>\n                      <div className='mb-4'>\n                        <span className='text-3xl font-bold'>{plan.price}</span>\n                        <span className='text-muted-foreground'>\n                          {plan.period}\n                        </span>\n                      </div>\n                      <ul className='space-y-2'>\n                        {plan.features.map((feature) => (\n                          <li key={feature} className='flex items-center gap-2'>\n                            <Icons.check className='text-primary h-4 w-4' />\n                            <span className='text-sm'>{feature}</span>\n                          </li>\n                        ))}\n                      </ul>\n                    </CardContent>\n                    <CardFooter>\n                      {isCurrent ? (\n                        <Button className='w-full' disabled variant='outline'>\n                          Current Plan\n                        </Button>\n                      ) : (\n                        <Button\n                          className='w-full'\n                          variant={plan.popular ? 'default' : 'outline'}\n                          disabled={\n                            loading || actionLoading === plan.name\n                          }\n                          onClick={() => handleUpgrade(plan.name)}\n                        >\n                          {actionLoading === plan.name && (\n                            <Icons.spinner className='mr-2 h-4 w-4 animate-spin' />\n                          )}\n                          {plan.name === 'free'\n                            ? 'Downgrade'\n                            : 'Upgrade to Pro'}\n                        </Button>\n                      )}\n                    </CardFooter>\n                  </Card>\n                );\n              })}\n            </div>\n          </CardContent>\n        </Card>\n      </div>\n    </PageContainer>\n  );\n}\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":1,"oldLines":53,"newStart":1,"newLines":278,"lines":[" 'use client';"," ","+import { useCallback, useEffect, useState } from 'react';"," import PageContainer from '@/components/layout/page-container';","-import { Card, CardContent, CardDescription, CardHeader, CardTitle } from '@/components/ui/card';","-import { useOrganization } from '@clerk/nextjs';","-import { PricingTable } from '@clerk/nextjs';","+import {","+  Card,","+  CardContent,","+  CardDescription,","+  CardFooter,","+  CardHeader,","+  CardTitle","+} from '@/components/ui/card';","+import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';","+import { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';"," import { Alert, AlertDescription } from '@/components/ui/alert';"," import { Icons } from '@/components/icons';","+import { authClient } from '@/lib/auth-client';"," import { billingInfoContent } from '@/config/infoconfig';"," ","+type Subscription = {","+  id: string;","+  plan: string;","+  status: string;","+  periodStart?: Date;","+  periodEnd?: Date;","+  seats?: number;","+};","+","+const plans = [","+  {","+    name: 'free',","+    label: 'Free',","+    description: 'For small teams getting started',","+    features: ['Up to 3 projects', 'Up to 5 members', 'Community support'],","+    price: '$0',","+    period: '/month'","+  },","+  {","+    name: 'pro',","+    label: 'Pro',","+    description: 'For growing teams that need more',","+    features: [","+      'Up to 100 projects',","+      'Up to 50 members',","+      'Priority support',","+      'Exclusive features'","+    ],","+    price: '$19',","+    period: '/month',","+    popular: true","+  }","+];","+"," export default function BillingPage() {","-  const { organization, isLoaded } = useOrganization();","+  const { data: activeOrg, isPending: orgPending } =","+    authClient.useActiveOrganization();","+  const [subscriptions, setSubscriptions] = useState<Subscription[]>([]);","+  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false)