{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Rkeaj7JRhH4UKYuQynM1hK","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have found all the profile-related files. Here's a summary of the profile/settings implementation:\n\n## Profile-Related Files Found\n\n### Main Profile Page\n**File Path:** `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/app/dashboard/profile/[[...profile]]/page.tsx`\n\n```typescript\nimport ProfileViewPage from '@/features/profile/components/profile-view-page';\n\nexport const metadata = {\n  title: 'Dashboard : Profile'\n};\n\nexport default async function Page() {\n  return <ProfileViewPage />;\n}\n```\n\n### Profile View Component\n**File Path:** `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/features/profile/components/profile-view-page.tsx`\n\nThis component uses Clerk's `UserProfile` component:\n\n```typescript\nimport { UserProfile } from '@clerk/nextjs';\n\nexport default function ProfileViewPage() {\n  return (\n    <div className='flex w-full flex-col p-4'>\n      <UserProfile />\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n```\n\n### Profile Form Schema\n**File Path:** `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/features/profile/utils/form-schema.ts`\n\nContains Zod schema for profile form validation with fields for firstname, lastname, email, contact number, country, city, and a dynamic jobs array.\n\n### User Avatar Profile Component\n**File Path:** `/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/src/components/user-avatar-profile.tsx`\n\nA reusable component for displaying user avatar with optional user information display.\n\n## Key Findings\n\n1. **Clerk Integration:** The profile page uses Clerk's `UserProfile` component directly from `@clerk/nextjs`\n2. **Simple Implementation:** The current profile page is minimal, delegating all profile management to Clerk's 