{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01RQScAJTwH2bPBhiWqrcX9x","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01QzfUU6MMEGpbbScNDUo1i1","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/docs/auth_setup.md","content":"# Better Auth Setup Guide\n\nThis guide covers the setup and configuration of better-auth features used in this starter template.\n\n## Overview\n\nThis project uses [better-auth](https://www.better-auth.com/) — a self-hosted, TypeScript-first authentication library with zero vendor lock-in. Auth data is stored locally in SQLite via Drizzle ORM.\n\n## Core Files\n\n- `src/lib/auth.ts` — Server-side better-auth configuration\n- `src/lib/auth-client.ts` — Client-side auth client (React hooks)\n- `src/lib/auth-schema.ts` — Drizzle schema (generated by better-auth CLI)\n- `src/lib/db.ts` — Drizzle ORM instance with better-sqlite3\n- `src/app/api/auth/[...all]/route.ts` — API catch-all route handler\n- `middleware.ts` — Route protection using `getSessionCookie()`\n\n## Environment Variables\n\n```env\nBETTER_AUTH_SECRET=    # Required: Auth secret key (generate with: openssl rand -base64 32)\nBETTER_AUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000    # Base URL of your app\nDATABASE_PATH=./sqlite.db    # SQLite database path\n```\n\n## Plugins\n\n### Email & Password\n\nEnabled by default. Users can sign up and sign in with email/password.\n\n### Organizations\n\nMulti-tenant workspace management with roles: `owner`, `admin`, `member`.\n\n- Users can create and switch between organizations\n- Organization members can be invited and managed\n- Role-based access control for navigation and pages\n\n### Stripe Billing\n\nOrganization-level subscription management via `@better-auth/stripe`.\n\n```env\nSTRIPE_SECRET_KEY=    # Stripe API secret key\nSTRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=    # Stripe webhook secret\nSTRIPE_FREE_PRICE_ID=    # Price ID for free plan\nSTRIPE_PRO_PRICE_ID=    # Price ID for pro plan\nSTRIPE_PRO_ANNUAL_PRICE_ID=    # Price ID for pro annual plan\n```\n\n- Webhook endpoint is auto-configured at `/api/auth/stripe/webhook`\n- Plans defined in `src/lib/auth.ts` (free/pro tiers)\n- Subscription status used for RBAC plan checks\n\n## Auth UI Components\n\nThis project uses `@daveyplate/better-auth-ui` for pre-built auth components:\n\n- **Auth pages**: `<AuthView />` for sign-in, sign-up, forgot-password\n- **Profile**: `<AccountSettingsCards />`, `<SecuritySettingsCards />`\n- **Organizations**: `<OrganizationSwitcher />`, `<OrganizationsCard />`, `<OrganizationSettingsCards />`\n\nThe `<AuthUIProvider>` wraps the app in `providers.tsx` and provides auth context to all components.\n\n## Navigation RBAC\n\nSee `docs/nav-rbac.md` for the client-side navigation access control system using better-auth hooks.\n\n## Schema Management\n\nAfter modifying plugins in `src/lib/auth.ts`:\n\n```bash\n# Regenerate schema\necho \"y\" | npx @better-auth/cli@latest generate --config ./src/lib/auth.ts --output ./src/lib/auth-schema.ts\n\n# Push to database\nnpx drizzle-kit push\n```\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":150,"cache_read_input_tokens":59121,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":150},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ce8911dc-a828-4e89-bfb5-264eebf8fb2a","uuid":"a1cd28ee-acbc-4cac-b49c-5c9aa453dc7d"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01QzfUU6MMEGpbbScNDUo1i1","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/docs/auth_setup.md"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ce8911dc-a828-4e89-bfb5-264eebf8fb2a","uuid":"4d38bb4d-0ab0-47fe-9981-f746f1a2dce0","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/bogdantarasenko/Desktop/hackinterview-tool/next-shadcn-dashboard-starter/docs/auth_setup.md","content":"# Better Auth Setup Guide\n\nThis guide covers the setup and configuration of better-auth features used in this starter template.\n\n## Overview\n\nThis project uses [better-auth](https://www.better-auth.com/) — a self-hosted, TypeScript-first authentication library with zero vendor lock-in. Auth data is stored locally in SQLite via Drizzle ORM.\n\n## Core Files\n\n- `src/lib/auth.ts` — Server-side better-auth configuration\n- `src/lib/auth-client.ts` — Client-side auth client (React hooks)\n- `src/lib/auth-schema.ts` — Drizzle schema (generated by better-auth CLI)\n- `src/lib/db.ts` — Drizzle ORM instance with better-sqlite3\n- `src/app/api/auth/[...all]/route.ts` — API catch-all route handler\n- `middleware.ts` — Route protection using `getSessionCookie()`\n\n## Environment Variables\n\n```env\nBETTER_AUTH_SECRET=    # Required: Auth secret key (generate with: openssl rand -base64 32)\nBETTER_AUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000    # Base URL of your app\nDATABASE_PATH=./sqlite.db    # SQLite database path\n```\n\n## Plugins\n\n### Email & Password\n\nEnabled by default. Users can sign up and sign in with email/password.\n\n### Organizations\n\nMulti-tenant workspace management with roles: `owner`, `admin`, `member`.\n\n- Users can create and switch between organizations\n- Organization members can be invited and managed\n- Role-based access control for navigation and pages\n\n### Stripe Billing\n\nOrganization-level subscription management via `@better-auth/stripe`.\n\n```env\nSTRIPE_SECRET_KEY=    # Stripe API secret key\nSTRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=    # Stripe webhook secret\nSTRIPE_FREE_PRICE_ID=    # Price ID for free plan\nSTRIPE_PRO_PRICE_ID=    # Price ID for pro plan\nSTRIPE_PRO_ANNUAL_PRICE_ID=    # Price ID for pro annual plan\n```\n\n- Webhook endpoint is auto-configured at `/api/auth/stripe/webhook`\n- Plans defined in `src/lib/auth.ts` (free/pro tiers)\n- Subscription status used for RBAC plan checks\n\n## Auth UI Components\n\nThis project uses `@daveyplate/better-auth-ui` for pre-built auth components:\n\n- **Auth pages**: `<AuthView />` for sign-in, sign-up, forgot-password\n- **Profile**: `<AccountSettingsCards />`, `<SecuritySettingsCards />`\n- **Organizations**: `<OrganizationSwitcher />`, `<OrganizationsCard />`, `<OrganizationSettingsCards />`\n\nThe `<AuthUIProvider>` wraps the app in `providers.tsx` and provides auth context to all components.\n\n## Navigation RBAC\n\nSee `docs/nav-rbac.md` for the client-side navigation access control system using better-auth hooks.\n\n## Schema Management\n\nAfter modifying plugins in `src/lib/auth.ts`:\n\n```bash\n# Regenerate schema\necho \"y\" | npx @better-auth/cli@latest generate --config ./src/lib/auth.ts --output ./src/lib/auth-schema.ts\n\n# Push to database\nnpx drizzle-kit push\n```\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
